1. Bank can be added alone, but to add Branch,
existence of Bank is mandatory!!! 

2. Customer and one Account is added together while adding Customer
More accounts can be added for a particular Customer later 

3. To add loan, existence of branch is mandatory!!! 

4. Deleting branch will also delete all loans as well as customers!!

5. Deleting bank will also delete all related :

customers--accounts 
and 
branches-->loans
 
 6. Deleting customer will delete all related accounts,
 but not loans!!!